metadata.name: Fearless Honey Badger Squad #1
metadata.description: Fearless Honey Badger is a collection of 2525 unique, hand-drawn and randomly-generated NFTs. We took our inspiration from art & next generation technology. We wish to form and be a part of an exclusive community and carve out a niche for our community in the blokchain universe. By purchasing the Fearless Honey badger, you have entered our community with exclusive rights. Our hope is to create a true community and advance our community day by day. The fearless honey badger project is the beginning of a long road.
